---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="About"
  description="Ajay Malghan is an Indian-American artist working in cameraless photography, abstract and documentary image-making, film, and painting. Based in Rockville, Maryland."
>
  <section class="about">
    <h1 class="display about__h">About</h1>

    <div class="about__body prose">
      <p>
        I make art because I find an immense amount of joy in the process.
        Time has no significance or meaning when I'm in the act of creation.
        Some pieces take minutes, some take months. Rarely have I ever made a
        piece better by going back to it.
      </p>
      <p>
        Constant experimentation over the years has taught me that I'm
        capturing an energy. That energy used to be manic, angry and mostly
        confused, but something shifted once I stopped drinking and doing
        drugs. While I never created under the influence, ceasing to ingest
        toxic thoughts and substances removed a dense layer of fog between
        me and my creativity. Upon that layer burning off, I stopped chasing
        and learned to listen more intently.
      </p>

      <ul class="about__qa">
        <li><em>Why do I make art?</em> Because I love it.</li>
        <li><em>What is the point of this idea?</em> Finish it first, then ask.</li>
        <li><em>What am I going to do with it?</em> Who cares?</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        What drives someone to photograph sites of slave markets, put
        cheeseburgers in enlargers and record abrasive drone music?
      </p>
      <p>
        The answer is quite simple — highly sensitive people hear and see
        things which others can't imagine or grasp. It's why so many struggle
        with mental health.
      </p>
      <p>
        We feel everything and most of the time it's too much.
      </p>
      <p>
        I'm one of the fortunate ones who can use multiple mediums to make
        sense of the world and how I view it.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about__contact">
      <span class="about__contact-label">Contact</span>
      <a href="mailto:ajaymalghan@gmail.com" class="about__email">ajaymalghan@gmail.com</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .about {
    max-width: 64ch;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem) var(--page-x);
  }
  .about__h {
    font-size: var(--t-6);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-weight: 400;
  }
  .about__body { margin-bottom: 3rem; }
  .about__body p { font-size: var(--t-3); margin-bottom: 1.1em; line-height: 1.7; }
  .about__qa {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 1.5rem 0 2rem;
    border-left: 1px solid var(--rule);
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }
  .about__qa li {
    font-size: var(--t-3);
    color: var(--ink-dim);
    line-height: 1.55;
  }
  .about__qa em { color: var(--ink); font-style: italic; margin-right: 0.35em; }
  .about__contact {
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }
  .about__contact-label {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--t-1);
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  .about__email {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--t-3);
    color: var(--ink);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    padding-bottom: 2px;
    display: inline-block;
    width: max-content;
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease;
  }
  .about__email:hover { border-color: var(--ink); }
</style>
